{"word":"G4185 - πολυτελής - polytelḗs - pol-oo-tel-ace' - Costly","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πολυτελής</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">polytelḗs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pol-oo-tel-ace'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Costly</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"விலையேறப்பெற்ற - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"precious, excellent, of surpassing value of great price"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4183 - πολύς - polýs - pol-oos'/4183\">G4183</a> and <a href=\"#/G5056 - τέλος - télos - tel'-os/5056\">G5056</a>; <i>extremely expensive:</i> - costly, very precious, of great price.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}